{"id":8250,"date":"2026-01-26T09:40:21","date_gmt":"2026-01-26T02:40:21","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8250"},"modified":"2026-01-26T10:52:45","modified_gmt":"2026-01-26T03:52:45","slug":"uvinul-a-plus-mang-loc-uva1-ben-truoc-anh-sang","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/uvinul-a-plus-mang-loc-uva1-ben-truoc-anh-sang\/","title":{"rendered":"Uvinul A Plus \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVA1 b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng ch\u1ed1ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu Tinosorb S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e1 ch\u1eafn to\u00e0n ph\u1ed5\u201d, th\u00ec Uvinul A Plus ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia ch\u1ed1ng UVA1 \u2013 lo\u1ea1i tia th\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t, g\u00e2y l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA \u00e2m th\u1ea7m d\u01b0\u1edbi da. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a BASF (\u0110\u1ee9c), Uvinul A Plus hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c v\u00e0ng cho b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 UVA trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-uvinul-a-plus\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 Uvinul A Plus<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI c\u1ee7a Uvinul A Plus: Diethylamino Hydroxybenzoyl Hexyl Benzoate<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i: Uvinul A Plus (thu\u1ed9c BASF, \u0110\u1ee9c)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00f3m: M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi, h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UVA1 (340\u2013400 nm)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u1ed5 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5: C\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3ng 354 nm, gi\u00fap che ph\u1ee7 v\u00f9ng UVA d\u00e0i m\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc c\u0169 (Avobenzone, TiO\u2082) ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00fd: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i EU, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u00dac, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA M\u1ef9 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ecba (nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ch\u00e2u \u00c1). (12\/2025)<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: Ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u1edfi BASF nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a Avobenzone (Butyl Methoxydibenzoylmethane).<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-mang-loc-uvinul-a-plus\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Uvinul A Plus<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt\u00a0<\/b><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8255 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-3.webp\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Uvinul A Plus\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul A Plus h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tia UVA1 \u2013 lo\u1ea1i tia chi\u1ebfm g\u1ea7n 75% t\u1ed5ng n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tia UV \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7ng trung b\u00ec, l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u00e2y l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 quang h\u1ecdc, m\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n s\u1eafc t\u1ed1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul A Plus l\u00e0 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UVA1 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng tia UV th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n, kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00e2n r\u00e3 nhanh d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Avobenzone.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea5u tr\u00fac ph\u00e2n t\u1eed c\u1ee7aUvinul A Plus c\u00f3 nh\u00f3m diethylamino gi\u00fap \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh isomer h\u00f3a \u2013 nh\u1edd \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 duy tr\u00ec \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1edd ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac \u00e1nh n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8256 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-4.webp\" alt=\"C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Uvinul A plus\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-va-ket-hop-pho-bien\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf v\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn<\/b><b><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul A Plus th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ea1ng lotion, fluid, gel-cream ho\u1eb7c hybrid. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 to\u00e0n ph\u1ed5, n\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVB v\u00e0 UVA2 nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tinosorb S: t\u1ea1o ph\u1ed5 UVA\u2013UVB li\u00ean t\u1ee5c, t\u0103ng b\u1ec1n s\u00e1ng.<\/li>\n<li>Uvinul T 150 (Ethylhexyl Triazone): t\u0103ng SPF v\u00e0 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc.<\/li>\n<li>Octocrylene: h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng ph\u00e2n h\u1ee7y \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.<\/li>\n<li>ZnO\/TiO\u2082 (kho\u00e1ng): gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, d\u1ecbu da v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m b\u00f3ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Xem th\u00eam:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-chong-nang-pho-rong-mela-gsc\/\">kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng Mela Bright<\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dunguvinul-a-plus\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ngUvinul A Plus<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kem-chong-nang-co-uvinul-a-plus-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 Uvinul A Plus d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi l\u00e2u, m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1eafng g\u1eaft: nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng cao, Uvinul A Plus gi\u00fap gi\u1eef PA\/PPD \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh su\u1ed1t ng\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>Da \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 (n\u00e1m, PIH): UVA1 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m, n\u00ean kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng ch\u1ee9a Uvinul A Plus gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00e1m t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t.<\/p>\n<p>Da treatment (retinoid, acid)<b>:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> gi\u1ea3m k\u00edch \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 duy tr\u00ec hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chong-chi-dinh-hoac-han-che\"><\/span><b>Ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1eb7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7c hi\u1ec7u trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 da c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c \u0111ang vi\u00eam c\u1ea5p n\u00ean th\u1eed test v\u00f9ng nh\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a Uvinul A Plus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y cay m\u1eaft nh\u1eb9 n\u1ebfu thoa qu\u00e1 g\u1ea7n m\u00ed.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng g\u00e2y r\u1ed1i lo\u1ea1n n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9c t\u00ednh sinh s\u1ea3n trong li\u1ec1u d\u00f9ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu-nu-co-thai-va-cho-con-bu-co-dung-duoc-khong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<h2><b><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8257 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Uvinul A plus kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-5.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-5-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-5-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Uvinul-A-Plus-5-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/b><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Uvinul A Plus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i an to\u00e0n khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 d\u1eef li\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng thai nhi ho\u1eb7c s\u1eefa m\u1eb9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong thai k\u1ef3, c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kho\u00e1ng (ZnO, TiO\u2082) v\u1eabn th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-quan-bao-bi\"><\/span><b>B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n &amp; bao b\u00ec<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Uvinul A Plus b\u1ec1n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u0169, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n n\u01a1i kh\u00f4 m\u00e1t, tr\u00e1nh n\u1eafng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eady k\u00edn n\u1eafp sau khi d\u00f9ng. D\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa l\u1ecfng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 sau th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i, n\u00ean l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thoa. Bao b\u00ec l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 chai m\u1edd ho\u1eb7c tu\u00fdp k\u00edn kh\u00ed (airless) \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">St\u00e9phanie, P. (2025, July 7). \u201cDiethylamino Hydroxybenzoyl Hexyl Benzoate\u201d? Typology Paris. <a href=\"https:\/\/us.typology.com\/library\/what-is-diethylamino-hydroxybenzoyl-hexyl-benzoate-and-what-is-its-use\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/us.typology.com\/library\/what-is-diethylamino-hydroxybenzoyl-hexyl-benzoate-and-what-is-its-use<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u200c<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu Tinosorb S \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e1 ch\u1eafn to\u00e0n ph\u1ed5\u201d, th\u00ec Uvinul A Plus ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia ch\u1ed1ng UVA1 \u2013 lo\u1ea1i tia th\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u nh\u1ea5t, g\u00e2y l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 s\u1edbm v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA \u00e2m th\u1ea7m d\u01b0\u1edbi da. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a BASF (\u0110\u1ee9c), Uvinul A Plus [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8253,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8250","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8250","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8250"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8250\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8252,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8250\/revisions\/8252"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8253"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8250"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8250"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8250"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}